<p><strong>By Rachit Sharma</strong> · We publish 30+ SEO articles per month for businesses across 70+ industries — and we test AI marketing tools daily to do it. · Last updated: May 17, 2026</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Our Top Picks:</strong>
- <strong>Best overall:</strong> ChatGPT Plus — most versatile AI for copy, strategy, and research at $20/month
- <strong>Best for design:</strong> Canva Pro — AI design, Magic Resize, and brand kits for $15/month
