<h2>8. Notion AI — Best AI Marketing Tool for Planning and Documentation</h2>
<p>Notion AI adds artificial intelligence to the already-popular workspace platform. For $10 per month, you get AI-powered writing, summarization, translation, and brainstorming inside your marketing documentation.</p>
