<p><strong>Our Take:</strong> Notion AI is the best tool for marketing teams that live in documentation. If your content calendar, strategy docs, and SOPs are already in Notion, the AI add-on is a no-brainer at $10 per month. The writing quality is comparable to ChatGPT-3.5 — good for drafts, not final copy. The summarization is the standout feature. We save approximately 3 hours per week on document review using Notion AI summaries.</p>
