<p>The best AI marketing stack for under $50 is ChatGPT Plus ($20) + Canva Pro ($15) + Buffer ($6) + Brevo free — covering writing, design, social media, and email for $41 per month. This combination outperforms single all-in-one platforms that cost twice as much.</p>
